Class CustomEnchantment

java.lang.Object
org.bukkit.enchantments.Enchantment
me.hsgamer.paperenchantmentcore.CustomEnchantment
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.kyori.adventure.translation.Translatable, org.bukkit.Keyed
public abstract class CustomEnchantment extends org.bukkit.enchantments.Enchantment
A custom enchantment. Should have a Plugin constructor. Example: 
     public class TestEnchantment extends CustomEnchantment {
         public TestEnchantment(Plugin plugin) {
             super(plugin, "test");
         }
     }
